DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\n🎉 Join Us for Trivia Night! 🧠☕
 ️\nCome hang out and put your brainpower to the test at Trailhead — we
 ’re set up in the cozy back area of the coffee shop!\n🕡 Trivia kicks 
 off promptly at 6:30 PM\, so swing by a bit earlier if you'd like to grab 
 a drink or something tasty to eat before we get started.\n📍 Location:\n
 Trailhead Coffee\n127 San Marin Drive\, Novato\, CA\nBring your friends\, 
