SUMMARY:Whale Watching & Chowder Tasting in Mendocino 🐋
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\nA beautiful day of awaits you in the c
 ity of Mendocino as the grey whales return to the California coast! Enjoy 
 the best chowders of the area at Crown Hall Inc - 45285 Ukiah Street\, Men
 docino CA and vote for your favorite. Afterwards we'll take a walk through
  downtown towards the Pacific Ocean and look migrating whales while listen
 ing to live music along the way. There is also a wine walk through downtow
 n for those wanting to taste regional wines and food pairings. I will be g
 oing to Chowder tasting\, but feel free to buy tickets for the wine walk a
 s well. Feel free to bring a friend or two.\n\nTickets can be purchased at
  Whale Festival - Mendocino Chowder Tasting & Wine Walk\n\nDate: Mar 7 •
  11:00\n\nhttps://www.eventbrite.com/e/whale-festival-mendocino-chowder-ta
 sting-wine-walk-tickets-1979919544656?aff=ebdsshother&utm_share_source=lis
 ting_android&sg=24aee98a71300d82abc7a743814bb139d84e28fefcc673a731bc33a266
 b07c889d3f527a14e0bf42be707e8dc7d2ca931d2b03615937afa733e1d716e39bf5662873
 59b4b3b762d04fe0419fce
