SUMMARY:Raise A Glass- Wine Tasting Event
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\nEnjoy tastings from over 10 local wine
 ries with a commemorative glass\, hor d'ouvers and live music all for $30.
  Tickets sold at the door.\n\nLive raffle featuring winery donations in th
 e last hour to help raise money for local summer camp scholarship fund. Ca
 regiving also available for kids aged 3-8 for an additional fee\n\nDue to 
 a prior commitment\, I won't be able to make it until later in the day.
